OOC: I think the distinction between the two CR rooms is getting
sloppy.  I was under the impression Dinobot, Rodimus, and Kup followed
Salveo to the Auxiliary CR room.  Nightlight is in the medical room.
I think Kenzo just moved to the other room after Nightlight got out.
(there are only 2 chambers in the medical room)  Be careful.

BIC:

Perseus walked to the CR room and got into the chamber next to Salveo.
   The chamber read: 60 cycles.

Meanwhile...

Trelos stared at Blacknightmare, he had no idea Unicron was powerful
enough to create his own minions.

"So, are you saying you no longer wish to serve your master?"
